data.description: First owner of PERRY HOMES 2022 construction. Extended entry leads to open family room, kitchen and dining area with 12-foot ceilings throughout. Owner installed new water softener system. Kitchen features generous island with built-in seating space. Family room features wall of windows and a wood mantel fireplace. Primary bedroom features 12-foot ceiling and wall of windows. Dual vanities, garden tub, separate glass- enclosed shower and two walk-in closets in primary bath. A game room and guest suite with private bath add to this spacious four-bedroom home. Extended covered backyard patio. Mud room off three-car garage.
